description:
Spectre (2015)

Watch Spectre: Bond is back. He is in Mexico pursuing a hit man. He kills the man but not after making a scene. When he returns to England his boss M is not happy because a government man known as C is trying to shut down the 00 network and replace it with a new surveillance system which will essentially put a end to privacy. M tells Bond to stand down and he has Q inject him with a tracking device. Bond reveals to Moneypenny why he was In Mexico. He asks her to help him by getting some info on certain people. He asks Q to make sure no one knows he left the UK and went to Italy to talk to the hit man's wife. After talking to him he goes to meeting of an organization and when he's discovered they try to...

enjoy
